Each pool has a hot tub, but one was closed for maintenance.	We then went to the 2nd pool room the hot tub was hot and the pool was still kinda cold.	The pool area was clean and comfortable with a nice hot tub as well.	Since it was so hot during our stay, in the 100's, the indoor pool was very inviting.	The pool and hot tub are open until 1 am which worked great for us when we got in late.	The indoor pool/jacuzzi could really use some updating, ventilation, and bigger towels, but water was clean.